  "tooltip.backend": "Local: runs on this Mac (Apple Silicon, ~2 GB models).\nOpenAI Cloud: audio + transcripts are sent to api.openai.com.\nSwitching reloads the inference pipeline.",
  "tooltip.region": "EU/ICAO: ICAO Doc 4444 + EU 2020/469 phraseology, QNH in hPa, VRP-based arrivals.\nUS/FAA: FAA AIM / NAV CANADA phraseology, Altimeter in inHg, CTAF self-announce.\nDE/BZF: DACH (DE/AT/CH) phraseology with digit-by-digit speech and BZF terminology. Realistic simulation, not BZF exam preparation.\nSwitching reloads templates and flight rules.",
  "tooltip.start_mode": "Cold and Dark: powered-off cockpit at parking.\nEngines Running: warm cockpit at parking, ready to call Ground.\nReady for Takeoff: at the holding point, awaiting Tower clearance.\nApplies on next sim start.",
  "tooltip.skip_radio_power": "Enable if your aircraft does not report radio power correctly.\nRadio buttons and PTT will work without electrical power.",
  "tooltip.recovery": "If you forget an ATC call (e.g. 'Runway Vacated' after landing),\nthe system resets automatically after this time.\n\nBeginners: 50-60 sec (more time to think)\nExperienced: 15-20 sec (keeps the flow tight)",
  "tooltip.show_hints": "Show suggested pilot phrases for the current ATC situation.",
  "tooltip.debug_text_input": "Replaces PTT/Mic with a text input below the transcript.\nUseful on laptops without a headset or to isolate ATC logic from STT mistakes.\nPTT stays functional in parallel.\n\nShortcut: type 'REG' as a placeholder for your phonetic callsign.\nExample: 'Tower REG, ready for departure runway 14'.",
  "tooltip.enable_traffic": "Master switch for traffic advisories, landing sequencing and the\nrunway-occupied go-around trigger.\n\nRequires a traffic provider (LiveTraffic, xPilot, swift, X-IvAp,\nor native X-Plane AI) - without one the TCAS dataRefs stay empty\nand the subsystem is silent anyway.\n\nTurn off if you fly solo without traffic and want zero overhead.",
  "tooltip.disregard": "Clear current ATC dialog -- you can contact ATC again anytime",
  "tooltip.set_standby_format": "Set COM%d standby to %.3f",

